for having me.

98
00:06:14.642 --> 00:06:16.544
[TRANSLATING IN JAPANESE]

99
00:06:16.677 --> 00:06:19.580
This is Yamauchi Kazunori,

100
00:06:19.714 --> 00:06:22.183
