in 80 million players.

103
00:06:31.359 --> 00:06:33.194
[JAPANESE TRANSLATION
PLAYING OVER HEADPHONES]

104
00:06:33.327 --> 00:06:35.596
The realism, the physics...
[ENGINE STARTS]

105
00:06:35.730 --> 00:06:37.932
