122
00:07:30.918 --> 00:07:32.687
[SPEAKING JAPANESE]

123
00:07:32.820 --> 00:07:34.956
[IN ENGLISH]
And how do you suggest
we do that?

124
00:07:35.089 --> 00:07:37.358
By creating a contest

125
00:07:37.490 --> 00:07:40.528
