we would all be responsible.

147
00:08:48.863 --> 00:08:51.265
Yes, I understand. Yes. Yeah.

148
00:08:51.399 --> 00:08:54.435
The board has agreed to
move forward with your program

149
00:08:54.568 --> 00:08:56.170
