Hey, uh, tell Nissan I'll do it.

315
00:16:46.139 --> 00:16:47.307
I'm not spending another minute

316
00:16:47.441 --> 00:16:48.776
with this pretentious
clown show.

317
00:16:48.910 --> 00:16:50.979
