How we doing, gamers?

324
00:17:04.993 --> 00:17:06.093
[BUTTONS CLICKING RAPIDLY]

325
00:17:08.195 --> 00:17:09.831
Favorite sound in the world:
sound of clicking.

326
00:17:09.964 --> 00:17:11.733
