349
00:18:07.187 --> 00:18:08.488
No. It's a contest.

350
00:18:11.693 --> 00:18:12.994
Press "play," dude.

351
00:18:15.063 --> 00:18:17.264
If you're one of
the very, very few people

352
00:18:17.397 --> 00:18:20.001
