00:20:47.682 --> 00:20:49.550
AUDREY:
Hey.

410
00:20:49.684 --> 00:20:50.752
Hey.

411
00:20:50.885 --> 00:20:52.687
You having fun over here?

412
00:20:52.820 --> 00:20:54.555
[CHUCKLES]

413
00:20:54.689 --> 00:20:57.925
