00:20:58.059 --> 00:20:59.560
Yeah?

415
00:20:59.694 --> 00:21:02.395
We were just talking about,
uh, traveling.

416
00:21:02.530 --> 00:21:04.098
Oh, really?
Yeah.

417
00:21:04.232 --> 00:21:07.434
I don't know, do you ever just
want to pack a bag

418
00:21:07.568 --> 00:21:10.437
