they have good pizza.

426
00:21:27.121 --> 00:21:29.257
[LAUGHING]:
Yes. I've heard that, too.

427
00:21:29.389 --> 00:21:31.592
Yeah?
[LAUGHING]: Yeah.

428
00:21:31.726 --> 00:21:32.960
What about you?

429
00:21:35.428 --> 00:21:37.430
This is stressful.
[BOTH LAUGH]

430
00:21:37.565 --> 00:21:38.666
Um...

431
00:21:38.800 --> 00:21:39.967
Gun to your head,
what's one place

432
