433
00:21:41.536 --> 00:21:42.904
Tokyo. Done.

434
00:21:43.037 --> 00:21:44.138
Okay.

435
00:21:44.272 --> 00:21:46.439
Tokyo.
Tokyo.

436
00:21:46.574 --> 00:21:50.443
