of these sessions
I have to do.

554
00:26:15.209 --> 00:26:16.444
Oh.
You know?

555
00:26:16.577 --> 00:26:18.446
You think that's
why you're here?

556
00:26:18.579 --> 00:26:21.148
Not... Is it not?

