643
00:30:17.051 --> 00:30:20.120
You took this of me
when I was five.

644
00:30:20.254 --> 00:30:23.957
All I've wanted to do
since then is be a racer.

645
00:30:28.195 --> 00:30:30.230
I am doing it.

646
00:30:32.366 --> 00:30:34.335
Whether you believe in me
or not.

647
00:30:37.505 --> 00:30:39.406
[♪♪♪]

