in the world.

657
00:31:12.707 --> 00:31:15.844
You've overcome
incredible odds to be here.

658
00:31:15.976 --> 00:31:19.346
Now you stand on this track

659
00:31:19.480 --> 00:31:22.817
with enormous opportunity.

