734
00:34:59.067 --> 00:35:00.902
INTERVIEWER:
What do you think
about your competitors?

735
00:35:01.035 --> 00:35:02.269
JANN:
They're great.

736
00:35:02.402 --> 00:35:03.771
INTERVIEWER:
How about Matty?

737
00:35:03.905 --> 00:35:05.105
To each his own.

738
00:35:05.238 --> 00:35:06.574
