00:38:31.311 --> 00:38:32.580
You're coming into turn 15.

828
00:38:32.713 --> 00:38:35.149
It's got a late apex.
The exit tightens.

829
00:38:35.283 --> 00:38:37.450
You got to find
your moment to pass.

830
00:38:37.585 --> 00:38:38.953
Come on. What you got?
What you got? What you got?

