[LAUGHS]

867
00:40:01.035 --> 00:40:02.570
Uh, you actually got
a bit lucky.

868
00:40:02.703 --> 00:40:04.272
Yeah, I think I did.

869
00:40:04.404 --> 00:40:06.274
Clearly, I mean,
you haven't been

870
00:40:06.406 --> 00:40:08.576
