Right.

895
00:41:04.065 --> 00:41:05.333
But it felt like
they were glazed.

896
00:41:05.465 --> 00:41:06.968
Oh, they were glazed.
Yeah.

897
00:41:07.101 --> 00:41:09.469
They were glazed. How...
I mean, how do you know...

898
00:41:09.603 --> 00:41:11.038
