928
00:42:30.951 --> 00:42:31.919
[PATS ARM]

929
00:42:40.561 --> 00:42:42.396
[ENGINE ROARING]

930
00:42:45.566 --> 00:42:47.368
[CAR APPROACHING]

931
00:42:50.539 --> 00:42:52.206
[BRAKES SQUEAK]

932
00:42:53.374 --> 00:42:54.909
[ENGINE SHUTS OFF]

933
00:42:59.346 --> 00:43:02.416
